## Choose an integration mode

When you want to deploy Passenger to production, you may want to use Passenger together with a web server like Nginx or Apache. For this purpose. Passenger provides a number of *integration modes*. Each mode has its own documentation, covering *installation*, *usage*, *troubleshooting* and more.

